<pdd-reason>Applies simple refund policy contract rules for generated-test traceability.</pdd-reason>

<pdd-interface>
{
  "type": "module",
  "module": {
    "functions": [
      {"name": "validate_refund", "signature": "(charge_amount: int, refund_amount: int) -> str", "returns": "str"}
    ]
  }
}
</pdd-interface>

<contract_rules>
R1: The system MUST approve a refund amount that is positive and less than or equal to the original charge amount.
R2: The system MUST NOT approve a refund amount that exceeds the original charge amount.
</contract_rules>

Implement validate_refund for integer cent amounts.
